org.mule.transport.soap.axis.transport
Class VoidURLConnection

java.lang.Object
  java.net.URLConnection
      org.mule.transport.soap.axis.transport.VoidURLConnection

public class VoidURLConnection
extends URLConnection

A fake url connection used to bypass Axis's use of the URLStreamHandler to mask uris as Urls. This was also necessary because of the uncessary use of static blocking in the axis URLStreamHandler objects.
